Just finished Lisa The Joyful. What a ride. It was on my wishlist for ages. After claiming it fit free on Epic, it took another couple months till I got around to it. Worth the wait, no regrets. I won't say much but if you want Earthbound for adults with CPTSD, this is your game. I want you to go in as blind as I did. If I had to ask who is Lisa for a game and a half, you do too. ;)

For those who have played, any good fan game recommendations?
